column16: Will Venable grounds out softly, pitcher Onelki Garcia to first baseman Drew Butera.
Brandon Belt homers (16) on a fly ball to center field.   Gregor Blanco scores.
Tim Lincecum grounds out, third baseman Juan Uribe to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.   Nick Noonan to 2nd.
Ehire Adrianza grounds out, shortstop Nick Punto to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
